{"tid":509588,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"oice平台視覺小說《Free-lancer》","createTime":"2017-12-25T13:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T17:02:37.000Z","uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"253ff500f3e94edceccbf1a97dd20823a468f030","tid":509588,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210008_ee688969864b7870cf13996210891e85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210008_ee688969864b7870cf13996210891e85.jpg&h=e7dc795a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作品facebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2F&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=1bdff9f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【故事簡介】 <br />\n<br />\n這是一個無法離開手機的年代。無論吃飯、乘車、購物、供樓、搭艇洗頭、叫家鄉雞和修改會議規則，都能用手機完成。 <br />\n<br />\n而在這個與香港極度相似的城市，任何人想找Freelancer幫忙，抑或Freelancer想接工作，都能用「EC Freelance」這個App做到。人人輕鬆透過手機發委託或賺外快，手機，變得更加不可或缺。 <br />\n<br />\n阿堂是這城市的一個小市民，以全職Freelancer為本業。一天，他意外拾到一部發紅光的奇怪手機。同時，市內暗地發生著不同的罪案，這些罪案發生時，現場都閃現了異樣的紅光&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n一如以往的日常，意想不到的衝擊。隨著一個陰謀擴散蔓延，阿堂亦漸漸捲入事件的洪流之中&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n命運，從此徹底改寫。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【有乜特別】 <br />\n<br />\n- 香港團隊製作，「我自由我導」視覺小說創作比賽參賽作品。 <br />\n- 12萬字原創故事劇本，10話共26節。 <br />\n- 以oice平台製作，包含原創角色和原創音樂，結合oice素材庫製作。 <br />\n- 1 Good Ending、1 Bad Ending、2個角色結局（附結局圖），另有結局彩蛋。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【有咩原創角色】 <br />\n<br />\n直接用圖答你 <br />\n<br />\n仔仔 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210100_fe07eee1f0268775c646e844b05bff2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210100_fe07eee1f0268775c646e844b05bff2d.png&h=6e5c8548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青梅竹馬 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210116_d9b6f4554ead74cebd62effb6a671a52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210116_d9b6f4554ead74cebd62effb6a671a52.png&h=7bff15e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傲嬌 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210130_0b3e6157812098b352cdeefc6c06ce17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210130_0b3e6157812098b352cdeefc6c06ce17.png&h=2a0bfab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n御姐 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210145_9675c1ff34145d7b1a68d3ddb6c0e555.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210145_9675c1ff34145d7b1a68d3ddb6c0e555.png&h=f85ce5ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大叔 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210203_79d59b191996ede84d98442fd4613cb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210203_79d59b191996ede84d98442fd4613cb0.png&h=cd954a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有其他，貼住咁多先 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【其他遊戲截圖】 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210246_5f3b980f0213c331c10559468a556d31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210246_5f3b980f0213c331c10559468a556d31.png&h=986de9fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210309_9a11768d2c2eea7c331011b06a7d4eb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210309_9a11768d2c2eea7c331011b06a7d4eb2.png&h=912df618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210326_90aa8175bdb24d517b9651eb5942028d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210326_90aa8175bdb24d517b9651eb5942028d.png&h=cd339bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【講左咁耐，點玩先】 <br />\n<br />\n套作品在oice平台發佈，所以要dl oice呢個app先 <br />\noice係一個製作同觀賞視覺小說的網上平台，香港團隊搞，免費dl <br />\n<br />\nAN： <br />\n<a href=\"http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.oice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.oice&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=8756f8cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.oice</a><br />\nIOS： <br />\n<a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/oice/id1248232355?ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Foice%2Fid1248232355%3Fls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=670d1f42\" target=\"_blank\">http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/oice/id1248232355?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n裝左app之後，點呢條link <br />\n<a href=\"http://oice.app.link/free_lancer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foice.app.link%2Ffree_lancer&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=85263843\" target=\"_blank\">http://oice.app.link/free_lancer</a> <br />\n應該就會自動彈入去oice個app，直接睇到個故事 <br />\n（用電腦click會睇到第一話第一節，但睇唔到之後既章節） <br />\n<br />\n唔鍾意點條link，可以入oice app自己搵，封面圖係咁樣樣 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210422_1a8f685c15feef92820538fea13ff231.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210422_1a8f685c15feef92820538fea13ff231.png&h=d5d0118e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果在fb點條link，可能會去左一個咁既畫面 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210446_8d1e713769d527db2e65870145893168.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210446_8d1e713769d527db2e65870145893168.png&h=85483935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔駛理佢，點幅圖就會入app睇故仔 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【FAQ】 <br />\n<br />\nQ：咩係視覺小說？oice咩黎？點解要我dl oice先睇得？ <br />\nA：早排fb答過呢條問題，詳見呢度 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/posts/1175399769258774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2Fposts%2F1175399769258774&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=e9a8cbe4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/posts/1175399769258774</a> <br />\n<br />\nQ：個故事未出晒？ <br />\nA：聖誕節今日出到第8話，成個故仔有10話，今年內會出晒。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：點解我見到有《光輝歲月》同《小林正雪》既角色？係咪抄襲？ <br />\nA：呢個係用oice平台製作視覺小說的素材共享特色。oice素材庫有呢兩套作品的角色圖可以用（由原作者親自上載），同樣，《Free-lancer》的原創角色一樣可以在oice平台俾人用。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：睇左幾話，個app叫我課金先可以繼續睇！？ <br />\nA：oice app的免費觀賞有限額，睇左幾話，就要等兩個鐘先可以繼續免費睇落去。（而家推廣期間，等5分鐘就得）<br />\n慢慢睇，唔駛急。如果過咗推廣期，又好急想免費繼續睇，請留意下一條問題。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：唔想用手機睇，有冇其他方法睇到？（或者唔想等兩個鐘又唔想課金） <br />\nA：可以用電腦睇，但極唔建議。詳細見fb的置頂帖 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/posts/1173199092812175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2Fposts%2F1173199092812175&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=71fb28fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/posts/1173199092812175</a> <br />\n<br />\nQ：咁做乜要我用手機睇？ <br />\nA：因為用手機睇先有最佳觀賞效果，同埋可以俾到製作團隊實質支持（非課金，見下條問題），詳見fb帖文解釋 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/posts/1175399769258774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2Fposts%2F1175399769258774&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=e9a8cbe4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/posts/1175399769258774</a> <br />\n<br />\nQ：個故仔好好睇！好想支持你！ <br />\nA：感謝！如果你喜歡呢個故事，我地誠意請求你，在oice app入面俾一個心心我地 <br />\n首先入oice app，點左下角的圓圈，用google account登入 <br />\n然後在《Free-lancer》的故事入面，將個心心點成紅色（見下圖） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/210550_ec44744ab36e8094482d9fd6d0f703b8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F210550_ec44744ab36e8094482d9fd6d0f703b8.jpeg&h=50029946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係本作在oice平台的人氣證明，非常重要，感激！ <br />\n<br />\nQ：個故仔好垃圾！收皮啦！ <br />\nA：謝謝你，如果有任何意見，歡迎喺度同我地講，或者去fb講都得。 <br />\n我們一定會汲取教訓，努力改進。"},{"pid":"f2a5dda3f54a43932a2860cb609329d2f927bee9","tid":509588,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaac5d26f649c9549105e79bc57e8922cc0e672","tid":509588,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2995a0c6f52e10a06dd150d81575539f563391be","tid":509588,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3f1d58ea7393188c5522817cfa296acca104e4","tid":509588,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}